                        "name": "Dazzling Burst",
                        "type": "offensive_action",
                        "text": "The d'ziriak causes its body to flare with intense colorful light. Non-d'ziriaks in a 20-foot emanation must attempt a DC 20 Fortitude save. After using this ability, the d'ziriak loses its glow for 24 hours; during this time it can't use Dazzling Burst again. A creature that attempts this save is immune to all Dazzling Bursts for 1 minute. <br/><b>Critical Success </b>The creature is unaffected. <br/><b>Success </b>The creature is <a aonid=\"7\" game-obj=\"Conditions\">dazzled</a> for 1 round. <br/><b>Failure </b>The creature is dazzled for 1 minute. <br/><b>Critical Failure </b>The creature is <a aonid=\"1\" game-obj=\"Conditions\">blinded</a> for 1 round and dazzled for 1 minute.",
